{
  "info": {
    "name": "Raag App — Course video bookmarks",
    "description": "Learner-only **`/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks`** (three endpoints).\n\n| Method | Path | Body / query |\n|--------|------|----------------|\n| **GET** | `/` | `page`, `limit` (optional) |\n| **POST** | `/` | **`title`**, **`videoUrl`** (required), **`description`** optional — **`userId`** from JWT |\n| **DELETE** | `/:id` | — |\n\nSet **`baseUrl`**, **`access_token`** (user login). **`course_video_bookmark_id`** is set by tests after list or add.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "course_video_bookmark_id", "value": "" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Get my bookmarks",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    const j = pm.response.json();",
              "    if (j.bookmarks && j.bookmarks.length && j.bookmarks[0]._id) {",
              "        pm.collectionVariables.set('course_video_bookmark_id', j.bookmarks[0]._id);",
              "    }",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks?page=1&limit=20",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "course-video-bookmarks"],
          "query": [
            { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
            { "key": "limit", "value": "20" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Add bookmark",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
              "    const j = pm.response.json();",
              "    if (j.bookmark && j.bookmark._id) {",
              "        pm.collectionVariables.set('course_video_bookmark_id', j.bookmark._id);",
              "    }",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Saved lesson\",\n  \"videoUrl\": \"https://example.com/watch.mp4\",\n  \"description\": \"Optional\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "course-video-bookmarks"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Delete bookmark",
      "request": {
        "method": "DELETE",
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks/{{course_video_bookmark_id}}",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "course-video-bookmarks", "{{course_video_bookmark_id}}"]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
